                "data_type": "complex ndarray, optional",
                "inline": [
                  {
                    "kind": "text",
                    "text": "If provided, the result will be placed in this array. It should be\nof the appropriate shape and dtype for all axes (and hence is\nincompatible with passing in all but the trivial "
